def: A gorgonian coral having a horny axis.
The monthly courses of women; menstrual discharges; menses.
The act of presenting apetition; a supplication.
A consolidated annuity (see Consols); -- chiefly in combinationor attributively.
To bewilder.Intellects bemazed in endless doubt. Cowper.
The office of an usher; usherdom.
Shaped like a sandal or slipper.
The quality or state of being like a vulture; rapaciousness.

To move the body to and fro with short, writhing motions, likea worm; to squirm; to twist uneasily or quickly about.Both he and successors would often wriggle in their seats, as long asthe cushion lasted. Swift.
